name: AutoHelix
overview:
AutoHelix is the most innovative social shopping network on web for automotive aftermarket products.

With a mission to bridge the gap between manufacturers and consumers, AutoHelix revolutionizes the online shopping experience with an interactive platform and cutting-edge technology.

Through it’s intuitive search engine, intelligent resource system, and powerful shopping tools, customers are able to find exactly what they are looking for without ever leaving the site. AutoHelix’s web engagement system helps them understand customers more on a personal level which allows the company to provide the best value and service possible. With features such as social profiles to mobile applications, AutoHelix will soon be the social phenomenon of the automotive industry.
